    "time_stamp": "2020-01-20 09:38:07",
    "text": "to clarify from the get go `dnd_area` does not work in emails at this time.\n\nDrag and Drop Emails do not yet support templates. You can however create an email in the drag and drop editor save it and duplicate that as “template” for now.\n\nDrag and drop design manager template layouts, also are unrelated to the drag and drop email editor."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "dennis edson",
      "poster_handle": "dennis261"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-01-20 09:39:11",
    "text": "yeah.  i wasnt thinking of using `dnd_area`  I am doing as you suggest by building a \"template\""
  },
